meta {
  name: 05 - Week 2 Ingestion
  seq: 5
}

docs {
  Week 2 document ingestion + write-back + evidence. Real files under
  `public/`: intake_upload.php, lab_upload.php, extraction_review.php,
  evidence.php. Run "00 - Auth Bootstrap" first for `csrf_token`.

  Flow: upload (intake or lab) returns a 302 to extraction_review.php with an
  `extraction_id`; set that in the environment, then run Review → Edit → Lock.
  Uploads reference a fixture document — set `fixture_pdf` in the environment
  to a local PDF/image path, or use the module's tests/Seed fixtures.
}
